summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of East & West Green Lake Boulevard from No. 77th Street to No. 65th Street et al., in the City of Seattle, by grading under Ordinance No. 20607, creating Local Improvement District No. 2055 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
